QuestData.Title: Peace Offering
QuestData.Description: We could really use an ally to trade with, commander.$B$BThere's an arakkoa outcast living in the middle of a ravager nest northeast of here... do you think he might ally with us? He must have some sort of secret to keeping those ravagers at bay.$B$BI have one last crate of my Northshire Port. Maybe that will help convince him that we're friendly.
QuestData.LogDescription: Deliver the Crate of Northshire Port to Dusk-Seer Irizzar.
